        "type": "Non-Tech",
        "date": "August 8, 2025",
        "contents": [
          "For the students who have been shortlisted & waitlisted for interviews, please take utmost care of the following points:",
          "Report to LHC 2 at 8:30 PM from the front gate",
          "Identification cards will be issued to students and runners at the main entrance in front of the Kresit building.",
          "Entry will be allowed only to those with issued Identification cards. Anyone found entering the LHC without the issued Identification cards will be penalized. No one should exchange or remove their identification cards.",
          "Only shortlisted & waitlisted students and their respective runners are required to report to the venue. No other students will be allowed inside the Lecture Hall Complex.",
          "All information about interview timings will be provided only at the allotted venue. If the shortlisted student is not present at the allotted venue, his/her interviews will not be scheduled.",
          "It is mandatory to carry at least 3 printed copies of your resume.",
          "Students are required to dress in formals and must adhere to the Student Internship Policy 2025-26.",
          "Students and runners must mandatorily carry their official IIT Bombay ID Card otherwise entry will be prohibited. Re-entry will not be allowed for both students and runners once they exit.",
          "Candidates and runners are supposed to wear their issued ID Cards at all times inside the LHC. The candidates can take off their ID cards only for the duration of their interviews. If anyone is found not wearing their issued ID cards, strict actions will be taken.",
          "It is compulsory to carry your laptops (with webcam), mobiles, microphone, earphones and chargers. Make provision for backup internet connection as precautionary measures."
        ],
